  "commit_message": "fix: escape HTML in reporter assertion messages (#33416) (#33941)\n\nThe reporter's formattedMessage() splits assert command messages into\nstructural regex matches (e.g. ` with <svg>`) and value parts (wrapped\nin `**`). Value parts were already HTML-escaped via mdOnlyHTML, but\nstructural matches were concatenated verbatim into the string that's\nlater set via dangerouslySetInnerHTML, so HTML in unwrapped trailing\narguments (like sinon's calledOnceWith) was rendered as live markup.\n\nEscape the struc",
